        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Bright field images of Conostigmus albovarius (Dodd, 1915) male habitus, lateral view (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539644)." , "Figure 6. Bright field images of Conostigmus albovarius (Dodd, 1915) male genitalia. A Dorsal view (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539648) B Ventral view (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539649)." , "Figure 5. Bright field images of Conostigmus albovarius (Dodd, 1915) male. A Head and mesosoma, dorsal view (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539647) B Head and mesosoma, lateral view (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539646)." , "Figure 4. Bright field images of Conostigmus albovarius (Dodd, 1915) female. A Head and mesosoma, lateral view (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539643) B Posterior mesoscutum and anterior mesoscutellum showing areolate sculpture and metallic coloration (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539645)." , "Figure 1. Bright field image of Conostigmus albovarius (Dodd, 1915) female. A Head and antennae, lateral view showing antennae and scape coloration (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539641) B Habitus lateral view showing a variation in antennae coloration (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539639)." , "Figure 2. Bright field images of Conostigmus albovarius (Dodd, 1915). A Female head and frons, anterior view (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539640) B Male head and frons, anterior view (see https: // doi. org / 10.6084 / m 9. figshare. 1539642)." ;
